content: God Implored to Rescue His People from Their Calamities.
For the music director;  El Shoshannim; Eduth. A Psalm of Asaph.
Who leads Joseph like a flock;
You who are enthroned  the cherubim, shine forth!
Before Ephraim, Benjamin, and Manasseh, awaken Your power,
And make Your face shine , and we will be saved.
